    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a bespoke 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain structural rigidity. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are within tight tolerances. While the exterior shows minor road-derived character, the drivetrain remains exceptionally visceral and responsive. Ideal for the enthusiast seeking a driver-focused platform with sorted vitals.",
